{"tid":2355100,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"六旬漢疑受武漢肺炎影響滯留內地 單位被房署收回","createTime":"2021-01-06T02:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T06:14:56.000Z","uid":135867,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82fd7be1e32072ca0246b813c09f579b4337a62a","tid":2355100,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QguNxPgUsevnPDXWLs_Ziw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/a20dbdb0-4eec-11eb-aff6-a05baaaa1258\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQguNxPgUsevnPDXWLs_Ziw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2Fa20dbdb0-4eec-11eb-aff6-a05baaaa1258&h=6b119017&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Wsnuh.HacXb4sAwOz9V5BA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/7dc03910-4eec-11eb-b3bb-441911aade3d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWsnuh.HacXb4sAwOz9V5BA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2F7dc03910-4eec-11eb-b3bb-441911aade3d&h=a0a7dffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳景林邨一名女職員，於昨日（4日）下午5時許報警，指景榕樓21樓一個單位被人打開了門鎖，警員登樓調查後，發現是戶主因延誤交租，房屋署執行法例賦予權力，而戶主返回單位用自己方法打開單位大門，警方尚在調查事件，未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n該戶戶主年約60歲的黃先生表示，於去年2020年1月初往內地拜祭父母，豈料爆發疫情，香港人前往內地需要隔離檢疫14天，返回香港後亦需隔離檢疫14天，他的體力亦難以支持，亦沒有親友協助，所以專誠寫信給房屋署說明難處，他以為房屋署收到了信件，所以就沒有繼續留意；同時他指他的手機已經沒有通話費，所以聯絡不上房屋署。<br />\n<br />\n去年12月1日返港後，他獲悉居所已被房屋署收回，屋內家當全部被丟走，門鎖亦已更換，他向當區區議員張偉超求助，亦表示明白繳付租金是租戶應有的責任，無奈受新冠肺炎疫情影響他未能夠如期返港，區議員張偉超為他向房署寫信，希望可以獲得恩恤安排。近日因天氣寒冷，黃先生用自己的方法進入單位暫住避寒，現時單位內家徒四壁，只有一張床褥睡覺。<br />\n<br />\n東網已就黃先生的個案向房署查詢，正等候房署回覆。"},{"pid":"b942857cc5cfefae54b23258c8dab71db691d58f","tid":2355100,"uid":135867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:31:04.000Z","msg":"戶主返回單位用自己方法打開單位大門，<span class=\"red\">警方尚在調查事件，未有人被捕</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b685b34cf5f86e188ed9683bce07307ebc6f7de","tid":2355100,"uid":130079,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:34:21.000Z","msg":"真係賤種黎<br />\n<br />\n清完間屋轉個頭就一堆雜物<br />\n<br />\n賤種係製造雜物方面特別叻"},{"pid":"16ebd3289ceafd35803eea443fa4214e64ef93c1","tid":2355100,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:35:04.000Z","msg":"內你老母"},{"pid":"08c1d5ee493bd46bb042f87a969eaffb3fe52acd","tid":2355100,"uid":25794,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:35:36.000Z","msg":"原來自己爆門入去住就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3e035a6858bf7ce0f60b8580180ad52d7fb5ec","tid":2355100,"uid":357591,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"呢條友係大陸有樓啦！<br />\n<br />\n成年都可以唔駛番香港，又唔交租<br />\n房署收番間公屋好合理！<br />\n<br />\n又係生人霸死地，人人都濫用公屋福利"},{"pid":"9cc5175e0f1c57de93d751274fa175b11d9316b5","tid":2355100,"uid":81149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"如果間屋已經配左俾下一手點算<br />\n日日嗌生嗌死？<br />\n終止左租約就重新排過隊啦"}]}